doktora g&uuml;rr&uuml;&#328;,&nbsp;</b>sen garyn bo&#351;lugyny&#328;, kronik
garyn keselleri&#328;, herniasyon, alamatlary ba&#351;langy&ccedil; wagty
barlygyna &#351;ikesleri we operasi&yacute;alar barada talk gerek.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bar&#351;ynda&nbsp;<b>muayene,&nbsp;</b>lukman
herniasyon, postoperatif izleri, &#351;i&#351;kinlik barlygyny we asimetrik
g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;i tespit.&nbsp;P&auml;sgel&ccedil;ilikleri&#328;
&yacute;uwa&#351;-&yacute;uwa&#351;dan &ouml;smegi bilen, k&ouml;plen&ccedil;
&ccedil;i&#351;i&#328; &ouml;smegi seb&auml;pli i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328;
hereketi g&ouml;r&uuml;n&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Garny du&yacute;magy&#328; we
di&#328;lemegi&#328; k&ouml;megi bilen lukman i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328;
b&ouml;wetlenmegine we &ouml;smegine seb&auml;p bolan kesellere mahsus
k&auml;bir alamatlary kesgitle&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Lukman rektumy g&ouml;zden
ge&ccedil;irende, diwarlaryndaky &ouml;s&uuml;&#351;i we gany&#328; yzlaryny
kesgitlemek &uuml;&ccedil;in anusy&#328; i&ccedil; &yacute;&uuml;z&uuml;ni
du&yacute;mak &uuml;&ccedil;in ellikli barmagy ulan&yacute;ar.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Laboratori&yacute;a
g&ouml;zlegleri -&nbsp;<b>umumy we biohimiki gan synaglary&nbsp;</b>-
k&ouml;mek&ccedil;i h&auml;si&yacute;ete e&yacute;e bolup, n&auml;sagy&#328;
&yacute;agda&yacute;yny&#328; umumy agyrlygyna, metabolik bozulmalary&#328;
&ouml;s&uuml;&#351;ine baha bermek &uuml;&ccedil;in
ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Instrumental
g&ouml;zlegler&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328;
obstruksi&yacute;asyny anyklamakda esasy orny
e&yacute;ele&yacute;&auml;r:&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Garyn rentgen &#351;&ouml;hlesi&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>- i&ccedil;egelerde
gazy&#328; we suwuklygy&#328; &yacute;ygnanmagyny &yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;ykaryp biler.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Mundan ba&#351;ga-da,&nbsp;<b>barlaglar kontrast
seri&#351;desi&nbsp;</b>- bari&yacute; sulfaty&nbsp;<b>bilen&nbsp;</b>ge&ccedil;irilip
bilner&nbsp;.&nbsp;Bu rentgen &#351;&ouml;hlelerinde a&yacute;dy&#328;
g&ouml;r&uuml;n&yacute;&auml;n ak re&#328;kli suwuklykdyr.&nbsp;I&yacute;mit
si&#328;diri&#351; ulgamyny&#328; &yacute;okarky b&ouml;leklerini &ouml;wrenmek
&uuml;&ccedil;in n&auml;saga i&ccedil;mek &uuml;&ccedil;in bari&yacute;
garyndysy beril&yacute;&auml;r we kontrasty&#328; i&ccedil;egelerden
n&auml;hili ge&ccedil;&yacute;&auml;ndigini synlamak bilen d&uuml;rli
aralyklarda suratlar alyn&yacute;ar.&nbsp;<b>I&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&nbsp;</b>barlamak
&uuml;&ccedil;in&nbsp;<b>suwary&#351; barlagy&nbsp;</b>ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r&nbsp;.&nbsp;Onu&#328;
dowamynda, kontrast anusy&#328; &uuml;sti bilen bir d&uuml;w&uuml;rtik ulanyp,
i&ccedil;ege sanjym edil&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bari&yacute;i&#328;
i&ccedil;egelerden ge&ccedil;megini&#328; bozulmagy
p&auml;sgel&ccedil;iligi&#328; alamatydyr.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Rentgeni&#328; netijeleri &#351;&uuml;bheli bolsa,&nbsp;<b>hasaplanan&nbsp;</b>&yacute;a-da&nbsp;<b>magnit-rezonans
tomografi&yacute;asy&nbsp;</b>&yacute;erine
&yacute;etiril&yacute;&auml;r&nbsp;.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>-Nji &yacute;ylda&nbsp;<b>Kolonoskopi, bir&nbsp;</b>kamera we
y&#351;yk &ccedil;e&#351;mesi in&ccedil;e tubular an&uuml;s arkaly &uuml;st
oturdylandan.&nbsp;Lukman bu enjamy ulanyp, i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; &auml;hli
l&yacute;umenini barlap biler, &ccedil;i&#351;i&#328; emele geli&#351;ini
kesgitl&auml;p we i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; daral&yacute;an l&yacute;ubenine
bir turba salyp, i&ccedil;ind&auml;ki zatlary&#328; hereketini
&yacute;e&#328;ille&#351;direr we &yacute;iti i&ccedil;ege b&ouml;wetlerini
a&yacute;yryp biler.&nbsp;Bu hassany &ccedil;i&#351;leri a&yacute;yranda
&ouml;r&auml;n m&ouml;h&uuml;m bolan me&yacute;ille&#351;dirilen
operasi&yacute;a doly ta&yacute;&yacute;arlamaga wagt
ber&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi maksatlary</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Mazmuny&#328; i&ccedil;ege
arkaly ge&ccedil;megine p&auml;sgel&ccedil;ilikleri &yacute;ok etmek,
m&uuml;mkin bolsa, &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykmagyny&#328; seb&auml;bini
&yacute;ok etmek, &#351;e&yacute;le hem kyn&ccedil;ylyklary&#328;
d&ouml;remegini&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351;
&yacute;oly we gurallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Uteiti i&ccedil;ege
obstruksi&yacute;asyny bejermekde olary&#328; &auml;hmi&yacute;eti
&yacute;ok.&nbsp;I&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; patensi&yacute;asyny
b&ouml;lekle&yacute;in bozan we hassany me&yacute;ille&#351;dirilen
operasi&yacute;a ta&yacute;&yacute;arlan &yacute;agda&yacute;ynda, az
i&yacute;mitlenmegi, tabak &yacute;um&#351;adyjylaryny kabul etmegi maslahat
beril&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Dermanlar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Gusmak, i&ccedil;egelerde &yacute;ygnanan i&yacute;mit
k&ouml;p&ccedil;&uuml;liginden z&auml;herli maddalary&#328;
bakteri&yacute;alary&#328; t&auml;siri astynda &ccedil;&uuml;&yacute;r&auml;p
ba&#351;lamagy seb&auml;pli &ouml;s&yacute;&auml;n serho&#351;lyga, suwsuzlyga
we metabolik bozulmalara gar&#351;y g&ouml;re&#351;i&#328;.&nbsp;N&auml;saglara&nbsp;<b>suwuklyklara
wena i&ccedil;ine infuzi&yacute;a,&nbsp;</b>mikroelementler bilen
erginler&nbsp;beril&yacute;&auml;r&nbsp;.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Peristaltikany&#328; k&ouml;pelmegi we garyn bo&#351;lugyny&#328;
agyrmagy bilen&nbsp;<b>antispazmodikler&nbsp;</b>, mysal &uuml;&ccedil;in,
&#351;pu &yacute;ok.&nbsp;Munu&#328; tersine, i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328;
gysylmagy bolmadyk &yacute;agda&yacute;ynda hereketi&nbsp;<b>gyjyndyryjy&nbsp;</b>ulanylyp
bilner&nbsp;.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Antibiotikler&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&yacute;okan&ccedil;
kyn&ccedil;ylyklary&#328; d&ouml;remegini&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak
&uuml;&ccedil;in ulanyl&yacute;ar&nbsp;.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Nazogastriki turbany oturtmak&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>-
a&#351;gazany&#328; we i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; p&auml;sgel&ccedil;ilikleri
seb&auml;pli &yacute;ygnanan zatlary a&yacute;yrmak &uuml;&ccedil;in
burnu&#328; a&#351;gazana&nbsp;<b>salyn&yacute;an&nbsp;</b>in&ccedil;e
turba.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Enemalary arassalamak&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>, k&auml;bir halatlarda
i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; b&ouml;wetlenmegini&#328; seb&auml;bini &yacute;ok
edip biler, &#351;e&yacute;le hem hassany kolonoskopi&yacute;a
ta&yacute;&yacute;arlap biler.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Hirurgiki amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Laparoskopiki
hirurgi&yacute;a&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:
"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>(&yacute;agny, deri de&#351;ikleri arkaly
d&auml;l-de, kesi&#351; d&auml;l) esasan &yacute;elim keseli &uuml;&ccedil;in
edil&yacute;&auml;r, di&#328;e k&auml;bir
&yacute;agda&yacute;larda.&nbsp;K&ouml;plen&ccedil;&nbsp;<b>laparotomi&yacute;a&nbsp;</b>edil&yacute;&auml;r
- garyn bo&#351;lugyny&#328; &ouml;&#328; tarapy
kesil&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Go&#351;uly&#351;ma umumy n&auml;gilelik astynda
amala a&#351;yryl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Operasi&yacute;a wagtynda hirurg di&#328;e
bir i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; b&ouml;wetlenmesini &yacute;ok etmek bilen
&ccedil;&auml;klenm&auml;n, onu&#328; &ouml;smegine seb&auml;p bolan keseli
&yacute;ok etm&auml;ge synany&#351;malydyr.&nbsp;P&auml;sgel&ccedil;ilik
&yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykarylandan we &yacute;ok edilenden so&#328;, hirurg
zeper &yacute;eten i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; &yacute;a&#351;a&yacute;y&#351;
ukyplylygyny barla&yacute;ar we zerur bolsa onu&#328; bir b&ouml;legini
a&yacute;yr&yacute;ar.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351;y&#328; hilini
dikeltmek we gowula&#351;dyrmak</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Operasi&yacute;adan so&#328; birn&auml;&ccedil;e
g&uuml;n&uuml;&#328; dowamynda n&auml;sag, adat&ccedil;a,&nbsp;<b>damar
i&yacute;mitleni&#351;inde bol&yacute;ar&nbsp;</b>, seb&auml;bi bu
d&ouml;w&uuml;rde i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; hereketi henizem
dikeldilme&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>N&auml;saglary&#328; bejergisinde m&ouml;h&uuml;m orny
&yacute;eterlik&nbsp;<b>simptomatiki bejergisi&nbsp;</b>, meselem, agyry
sindromyny &yacute;ok etmek&nbsp;e&yacute;ele&yacute;&auml;r&nbsp;.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>K&auml;bir &yacute;agda&yacute;larda, k&ouml;plen&ccedil;
p&auml;sgel&ccedil;ilik d&ouml;red&yacute;&auml;n &ccedil;i&#351;
seb&auml;pleri bilen, operasi&yacute;adan so&#328;&nbsp;<b>stomany&nbsp;</b>a&yacute;yrmak
zerur bolup biler&nbsp;.&nbsp;Bu &yacute;agda&yacute;da
i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; so&#328;ky b&ouml;l&uuml;mi, kolostomi&yacute;a
sumkasy dakyl&yacute;an garny&#328; &ouml;&#328; diwarynda
g&ouml;rkezil&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Stoma wagtla&yacute;yn &yacute;a-da
hemi&#351;elik bolup biler.&nbsp;Saglygy gora&yacute;y&#351;
i&#351;g&auml;rleri hassany stoma bilen n&auml;dip dolandyrmalydygyny we
&yacute;a&#351;amalydygyny &ouml;wretmeli.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Operasi&yacute;adan so&#328; hassany gysga wagtda&nbsp;<b>i&#351;je&#328;le&#351;dirmeli&nbsp;</b>,
bu k&ouml;p kyn&ccedil;ylyklary&#328; we my&#351;salary&#328; gow&#351;aklygyny
peseld&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>M&uuml;mkin kyn&ccedil;ylyklar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>I&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; bir b&ouml;legini&#328;&nbsp;<b>nekrozy&nbsp;</b>(&ouml;l&uuml;mi).&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
